00:39:59,100 --> 00:40:01,330
But you and I owe each other nothing anymore.

290
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,700
Whoever has wronged me

291
00:40:39,970 --> 00:40:41,700
I’ll repay it a thousandfold.

292
00:40:43,930 --> 00:40:44,730
Let’s go.

293
00:40:45,100 --> 00:40:46,170
I can walk myself.

294
00:40:48,930 --> 00:40:50,130
Wait, officer.

295
00:40:55,370 --> 00:40:56,170
Don’t be afraid.

296
00:40:57,300 --> 00:40:59,000
Just tell the whole truth.

297
00:41:00,070 --> 00:41:01,870
Khun Sasom will make sure you’re safe.

298
00:41:03,530 --> 00:41:04,050
Yes.

299
00:41:04,680 --> 00:41:06,150
And I’ll tell the truth about everything.

300
00:41:07,570 --> 00:41:08,180
Good.

301
00:41:08,950 --> 00:41:13,050
Go ahead, officer. I won’t interfere.

302
00:41:13,050 --> 00:41:13,550
Yes.

303
00:41:13,550 --> 00:41:14,050
Go.

304
00:41:24,970 --> 00:41:27,400
What about that one of Khun Sasom’s?

305
00:41:28,500 --> 00:41:29,300
You mean…

306
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:35,100
That matter.

307
00:41:35,970 --> 00:41:37,600
Don’t make me say it.

308
00:41:38,670 --> 00:41:39,530
Honestly,

309
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:40,800
just thinking about it

310
00:41:41,330 --> 00:41:42,930
already makes me uncomfortable as hell.

311
00:41:43,930 --> 00:41:44,870
It’s nothing.

312
00:41:45,570 --> 00:41:46,730
Khun Po is safe.

313
00:41:47,100 --> 00:41:47,900
Really?

314
00:41:48,170 --> 00:41:48,970
Yes.

315
00:41:50,970 --> 00:41:51,770
What a relief.

316
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:53,200
Phew…

317
00:41:53,300 --> 00:41:54,100
That’s good.

318
00:41:54,270 --> 00:41:55,330
That person is safe.

319
00:42:06,170 --> 00:42:09,670
I hope Khun Po and Khun Sasom finally find happiness.

320
00:43:19,700 --> 00:43:21,130
You’re giving this to me?

321
00:43:24,070 --> 00:43:24,870
Yes.

322
00:43:56,070 --> 00:43:56,870
Do you like it?

323
00:44:01,500 --> 00:44:02,300
I do.

324
00:44:03,800 --> 00:44:05,100
I like it very much.

325
00:44:07,600 --> 00:44:08,400
Actually,

326
00:44:09,200 --> 00:44:11,670
this is the first gift I’ve ever received.

327
00:46:24,070 --> 00:46:25,600
Tell me if anything hurts.

328
00:46:30,400 --> 00:46:31,690
I’m okay.

329
00:46:33,500 --> 00:46:35,580
I was just a little startled.

330
00:46:49,070 --> 00:46:50,500
After what they did to us,

331
00:46:53,170 --> 00:46:54,900
this isn’t something small anymore.

332
00:47:25,470 --> 00:47:26,530
Get well soon, sweetheart.

333
00:47:35,400 --> 00:47:36,200
Thank you.

334
00:48:10,000 --> 00:48:11,200
It’s okay.

335
00:48:14,270 --> 00:48:15,500
I’m here now.

336
00:48:18,270 --> 00:48:20,270
I won’t let anyone hurt you again.

337
00:48:30,600 --> 00:48:32,630
You’re not angry with me, right?

338
00:48:34,050 --> 00:48:36,010
For making you worry.

339
00:48:43,600 --> 00:48:45,730
You can hold me all night tonight.

340
00:48:48,000 --> 00:48:49,330
You don’t have to be afraid anymore.

341
00:49:30,870 --> 00:49:32,310
From now on,

342
00:49:34,360 --> 00:49:36,060
I’ll take good care of you.

343
00:50:23,470 --> 00:50:25,470
Today I thought I wouldn’t survive.

344
00:50:27,670 --> 00:50:29,410
I never thought

345
00:50:30,770 --> 00:50:33,310
there would be a day I’d face my own father

346
00:50:35,400 --> 00:50:38,130
who treated me like a toy in his hands.

347
00:50:39,970 --> 00:50:41,500
But because of this,

348
00:50:41,870 --> 00:50:43,130
I realized

349
00:50:45,770 --> 00:50:47,330
I was never alone.

350
00:50:49,200 --> 00:50:50,460
He came to help me,

351
00:50:50,990 --> 00:50:53,040
even though his life was at risk too.

352
00:50:55,170 --> 00:50:56,470
It made me realize

353
00:51:01,330 --> 00:51:03,400
no matter how cruel this world is,

354
00:51:05,470 --> 00:51:06,870
I still want to stay here.

355
00:51:14,400 --> 00:51:16,780
But I can’t help wondering

356
00:51:19,750 --> 00:51:23,350
how long this happiness will stay with me.

357
00:51:28,500 --> 00:51:30,100
And if one day it disappears,

358
00:51:31,300 --> 00:51:32,970
will I really be ready for it?

359
00:52:19,530 --> 00:52:21,420
I want to go buy a Christmas tree.

360
00:52:22,290 --> 00:52:24,600
Merry Christmas.

361
00:52:24,600 --> 00:52:25,460
Yay!

362
00:52:33,970 --> 00:52:35,120
Hello everyone.

363
00:52:35,610 --> 00:52:37,110
It’s been a long time.

364
00:52:38,280 --> 00:52:40,840
But I have to tell everyone honestly that…

365
00:52:41,960 --> 00:52:43,890
I can’t do this anymore.
